      <abstract>Clarendon Congregational Church was located in Hyde Park Boston, Massachusetts. The
        church was organized in 1880 and dissolved circa 1964. This collection houses administrative
        records including church records, meeting minutes, and scrapbooks from Clarendon
        Congregational Church.</abstract>
